.DT 
init_command 
Discworld monster help 
init_command 

Name
.SI 5
init_command - Delayed command.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
varargs void init_command(string com, int tim);
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
Does the specified command after a delay of tim seconds.  ie does
a call_out of that many seconds.  This is used both to stop over
evaluation at the creation of a monster and to delay commands.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
do_command
.EP
